[0m[49m[39m  316, 321[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      322[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         // --- Randomization holdout ---
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      323[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         // Reserve ~7% of balances for random strategy assignment.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      324[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         // This creates counterfactual data: what would have happened
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      325[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         // if we'd treated this balance differently? Essential for
